== 取消續集與重啟 ==
演員[[瑪麗亞·貝蘿|瑪麗亞·貝蘿]]在訪談中表示，《神鬼傳奇》將很有可能拍攝第四集，且她也已經同意接拍續集，繼續扮演女主角艾芙琳的角色。<ref>{{cite news | language = en | author = Shawn Adler | url = http://www.mtv.com/movies/news/articles/1583041/story.jhtml | title = 'Mummy 3' Star Maria Bello Talks About Taking Over For Rachel Weisz, Fighting An Invisible Baddie | publisher = [[音樂電視網|音樂電視網]] | date = 2008-03-10 | accessdate = 2008-04-09 | archive-date = 2008-04-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080409231303/http://www.mtv.com/movies/news/articles/1583041/story.jhtml | dead-url = no }}</ref> 飾演歐康納兒子的{{Link-en|路克·福特|Luke Ford (actor)}}也同意拍攝多三部此系列的電影。<ref>{{cite news | language = en | author = MrDisgusting | url = http://www.bloody-disgusting.com/news/12932 | title = Luke Ford Signed For Three 'Mummy' Films | work =  | publisher = Bloody-Disgusting.com | date = 2008-07-16 | accessdate = 2008-07-20 | archive-date = 2008-07-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080720002349/http://www.bloody-disgusting.com/news/12932 | dead-url = no }}</ref>不過在2012年，環球影業宣佈已經取消該續集電影，取而代之正在計劃一套[[重啟|重啟]]。環球影業已經聘用{{link-en|乔·斯派茨|Jon Spaihts}}編寫劇本，並表示會比前集黑暗。<ref name=VR1118052291>{{cite news | title = U sets 'Mummy' reboot with Spaihts | publisher = [[綜藝_(雜誌)|Variety]] | date = 2012-04-04 | url = http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118052291 | accessdate = 2012-04-04 | archive-date = 2012-04-07 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120407021220/http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118052291 | dead-url = no }}</ref>{{Link-en|桑·丹尼爾|Sean Daniel}}回歸作監製。<ref name=VR1118052291/>[[羅柏托·奧契|羅柏托·奧契]]和[[亚里克斯·库兹曼|亚里克斯·库兹曼]]與環球影業簽署了兩年協議之後，將會以{{link-en|K/O Paper Products|K/O Paper Products}}的名義製作。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.imdb.com/title/tt2345759/trivia?ref_=tt_trv_trv|title=The Mummy (2016)|work=IMDb|accessdate=2014-10-06|archive-date=2016-01-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160108193029/http://www.imdb.com/title/tt2345759/trivia?ref_=tt_trv_trv|dead-url=no}}</ref>電影計劃在2016年6月24日發行，由亚里克斯·库兹曼執導。暫未公佈演員陣容。重啟版的《[[神鬼傳奇_(2017年電影)|神鬼傳奇]]》於2017年6月9日上映。

